    "Recent results reported that the attention-based models offered higher efficiency and better performance than convolutional and recurrent models in WPP tasks.",
    "To verify the performance advancement brought by deep learning methods, we surveyed the existing literature and reported the improvement generated by deep learning methods against traditional models.",
    "We further verify the effectiveness of recent WPP development via reproducing and comparing latest deep learning models based on SCADA datasets collected from three commercial wind farms.",
    "The results demonstrated that DLinear achieved better performance on all of datasets considered in this work.",
    "The Informer, Transformer, and GRU model could also obtain promising results."
